column5: Makes me want to tackle the mighty St Lawrence!
AndreThanks so much for posting that link, very informative and interesting to watch the progress of the Walleye moving out into deeper water.Jeff in Iowa

Very interesting. Sometime, i'd like to see a facsimile, except with corresponding weather conditions, which could be a big help for determining where to fish based upon what's going on outside. I think, maybe. Bill
